author: Al Jazeera
description: Deadly explosion at pop star Ariana Grande performance a 'terrorist incident' with dozens also wounded, UK police say.
title: Ariana Grande concert: Blast a 'terrorist incident'

author: Steve Robson
description: Witnesses reported hearing several 'explosions', which police said was in the foyer area, moments after the Ariana Grande gig finished
title: Follow updates after deadly explosion at Ariana Grande gig at Manchester Arena

author: Kim Hjelmgaard, and Melanie Eversley
description: Singer Ariana Grande is OK after reports of multiple explosions at a concert Monday in Manchester in the U.K.
title: At least 19 dead in fatal blasts at Ariana Grande concert in U.K.

author: Ben Westcott and Emily Smith, CNN
description: British police have confirmed 19 people have been killed in what's being treated as a terrorist incident at Manchester Arena, after an Ariana Grande concert Monday night.
title: Ariana Grande concert incident: Live updates

author: CNBC
description: At least 20 people were killed Monday night at an Ariana Grande concert at Manchester Arena in England, multiple law enforcement told NBC News.
title: At least 20 dead after explosion heard at Ariana Grande UK concert

description: A witness at Ariana Grande's concert inside of Manchester Arena in England said there were little girls crying after reports of an explosion inside the venue.
title: Witness at Ariana Grande event describes chaos - CNN Video

description: A blast at a concert in the northern English city of Manchester where US singer Ariana Grande had been performing left several people dead and injured, police said. Stay with TOI for updates.
title: Blast at Ariana Grande concert in British arena, several killed - The Times of India

author: Rachel Bishop, Stephen Jones
description: Hundreds of people fled the arena screaming after hearing 'loud bangs' at the end of an Ariana Grande concert - where many of the gig goers were young female fans of primary school age with their parents
title: Deaths at Ariana Grande gig as police treat blast as possible terror attack

author: Samantha Beech and Darran Simon, CNN
description: At least 19 people are dead and about 50 injured in a possible terrorist incident Monday at Manchester Arena in England, where pop singer Ariana Grande was performing, Greater Manchester Police said.
title: British police: 19 dead after blast at Ariana Grande concert in Manchester

author: Jon Super
description: A blast on Monday night at a concert in the English city of Manchester where U.S. singer Ariana Grande had been performing left at least 19 people dead and about 50 injured in what British police said was being treated as a terrorist incident.
title: At least 19 dead in blast at Ariana Grande concert in British arena
